{
  "stem": "19923.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he-- what he did is he sewed one into the lining of his clothes, and he sewed one into the lining of my father's clothing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he knew my father did not have the strength of character that he could stand there and answer the question and lie.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when the Gestapo finally came to my father-- no, first came to Uncle Charles.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Uncle Charles says, [GERMAN] mark, only have 10 marks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then they went on to my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my uncle tells the story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He grabbed my father by the hand-- and by the wrist actually, dug his nails into his wrist, squeezed so hard to give him courage.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my father said, 10 marks, and they passed him by.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after that, my father went back to his village in [NON-ENGLISH], and that's where he ended up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as the story will go later on, there will be discovered what happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In 1941, when they were rounding-- they rounded up all the Jews of that area and shot them in a mass grave.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My Uncle Charles, he had been to London the year before as a visitor in 1937.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And while there, he met his future wife.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they started corresponding during that year, and he started learning English.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when he got into Poland, he immediately used his money to go to Danzig, which is now Gdansk, and from there he caught a boat, and he caught a boat to London.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Gdansk-- Danzig was a free port.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So with the money, he was able to buy passage to-- to England, and he still had his visa from the year before.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when he got to London, he called, telephoned, Auntie Milly, and Auntie Milly's his wife.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
